Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:05.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个角笛是个护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着这个赶快从这里逃出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了　快点从这里逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你　这个东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:21.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会还给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天　一定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还给我　臭老爸 这是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.45,0:02:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…再不还我就……
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.05,0:02:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（我们的采访小组终于成功地拍摄到了\N流幻泽的巨大生物的影像了）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:02:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流幻泽？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.55,0:03:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（传说中的流幻泽巨大的魔物，确实存在）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个名字…好像在哪里……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.55,0:03:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛　这种东西你都相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.76,0:03:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:16.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得好像在哪听过而已……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能有那样的怪物呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是够幼稚的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶尔也该看看教做饭的节目吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.56,0:03:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.96,0:03:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干什么啊！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.36,0:03:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以前的家庭旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.06,0:03:35.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还去过流幻泽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯……不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯　而且当时小茜还迷路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你独自进了森林里　还怕得大叫了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇！爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说　那并不是梦了……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　我去接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好　这里是天道家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是　啊　消灭怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.97,0:04:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…什么地点？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流幻泽？！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱马1/2 特别篇\N苏醒的记忆（上卷）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.98,0:04:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是谁给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说这个角笛是什么护身符的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小……小茜……\N（我到流幻泽去了　不用担心　小茜）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜…………
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说小茜离家出走了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱马君　你不知道原因吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么是我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天说那种话……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛　这种东西你都相信？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.79,0:05:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才说了这点她就受不了要离家出走啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你昨天说那种话……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　乱马君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜她一向孩子气　任性　脾气又倔强……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着这么说啊　小霞……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但……但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界上怎么可能有那种怪物嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有哦　乱马君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱……马……君！！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 我马上就去！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里过河就是流幻泽了，
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.40,0:06:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物就在那里，麻烦你了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我就是在这里迷路的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　是那个男孩子……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.01,0:07:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:13.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错　是那个男孩救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.01,0:07:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就给了我这个角笛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.11,0:07:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.71,0:08:01.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我自己会处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:02.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物想袭击的只有你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……我是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再重复说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了　和那时候一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人就是……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.72,0:08:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去　接下来的我自己会处理……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来背你回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了……这就是这个男孩的家……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.43,0:09:26.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去消灭怪物了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.63,0:09:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　那个叫小茜的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说她是天道道场的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜那家伙到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:45.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:07.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座森林究竟……是怎么了……？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送真之介回来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这么说　是他救了我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他叫做真之介啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很感谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷卧病在床
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也忙于守护这座森林
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碍事的人是不是可以回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重拳击！！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:56.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思　真之介这孩子一个人\N在这里长大　不懂言辞礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他说的是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔一只怪物走到森林外面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.05,0:11:17.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都是我们这些森林居住者负责
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君　请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在守护着这森林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.35,0:11:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个……你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.75,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候……你给我的……
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,角笛护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没印象　你认错人了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.86,0:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了……诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.66,0:12:52.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:54.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一不留神就……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座森林很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.26,0:12:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　又不是我喜欢来这里！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.47,0:13:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过一个女孩子吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:08.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她应该已经进入这个森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:17.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗？再见了　谢谢你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点　这附近全是陷阱……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.47,0:13:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊　一时忘了这个女孩子在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.57,0:13:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对刚才的人做了坏事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你很健忘　但是你竟然能连爷爷都忘记了？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.57,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是我搞错了吗，真之介君？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.57,0:13:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救我的人难道不是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂　快点去洗澡吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　真之介君的样子不像是在说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:20.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么以前救过我的男孩子……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:23.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊……？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了　我还没洗澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了　这么胡思乱想也不是个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一时忘记你在洗澡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:53.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,背上的伤……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:15:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君就是那个男孩子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介啊　真之介……！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:23.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上　真之介的命很悬啊，
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事啊　爷爷？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介之所以能活到现在　\N全靠流幻泽的飞御森林里的生命之水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.59,0:15:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之水？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的　悠久的泉水中蕴藏着生命的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林里的动物都是受了生命之水\N的影响才如此巨大化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是　为什么人好好的　动物却……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们战胜了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是……是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和真之介作为这座森林的守护者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都和这些巨大化动物战斗　但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真……真之介！你怎么受了这么严重的伤……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么难道说……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的伤真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事　你快点回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个角笛是护身符　吹着它快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我发现他时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介他……已经奄奄一息了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:45.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使送往村里的医院　也肯定来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我情急之下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:53.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用生命之水挽回了真之介的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喔！真是奇迹啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:17:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介居然好起来了　真是多亏了生命之水啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到目前为止　看来那水能改变人的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命之水　赋予了生机啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.81,0:17:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是最近以来　生命之水产生了变化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失去了生命之水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.71,0:17:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介就无法活下去了……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎……怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:18:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介目前还不知道自己身体的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.02,0:18:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请尽量在真之介面前做出平常的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君背上的伤这么严重……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.72,0:18:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要做出精神焕发的样子！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好啊　真之介君！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.42,0:18:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介　不要抛下我一个人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要哭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.82,0:18:30.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.32,0:18:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是你的爷爷！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给　味噌汤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没什么信心保证味道……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.13,0:18:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎　挺香的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个……我是真的没什么信心，
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.43,0:18:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好吃的话……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.33,0:18:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:58.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从来没有尝过这么美味的味噌汤！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:18:59.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一碗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也还要一碗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎……请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很好吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.34,0:19:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是用生命之水做出来的饭菜啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一碗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:16.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.14,0:19:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在看起来生龙活虎……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来　我还不知道你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:27.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜　天道茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜……真是个好名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了　记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不着这样吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊　真之介君是我的救命恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次轮到我来救真之介君了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.85,0:20:00.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都叫我“耳梨保一”……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.45,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎哟……小茜到底跑到哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉　这次又是什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我出去看看情况
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这……这是……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说“它”苏醒了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.85,0:20:33.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？那家伙是昨天的……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真之介君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.66,0:20:36.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘记了这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋还说不知道什么女孩……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心一点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果方便的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能不能为我们做晚饭？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.36,0:20:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱马？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.67,0:21:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱马……你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个应该是我问你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这里干什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.77,0:21:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.87,0:21:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦　难得这么老实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总……总之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔他们都在担心你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:26.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.87,0:21:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊 我还得为他们做晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得很可笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界上有谁会喜欢吃你做的饭啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你尝尝看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个……是你做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃……这……这个……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊……如果真的是你做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭菜什么的还无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的巨大生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜的饭菜突然变得美味
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座森林一定有什么特别的秘密！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅仅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上……乱马……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.49,0:22:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和真之介君……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:22.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等……等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.39,0:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难不成你想说你不回去了吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.19,0:22:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要待在真之介君身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……听着……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.59,0:22:41.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做是有原因的……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:46.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱马？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉……乱马……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.10,0:23:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊……不得了啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:04.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泉水枯竭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.80,0:23:08.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛！什么嘛！！什么嘛！！！什么嘛！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道那个小子比我好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:14.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊！这样啊！！这样啊！！！这样啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.80,0:23:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小茜你这个大笨蛋！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.30,0:23:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,森林在下沉？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.10,0:24:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶！这里究竟是什么地方啊！
